
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>DIAMOND TOP UP MM - PREMIUM</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #0b0f19; 
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 50% 0%, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.18) 0px, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, rgba(0, 245, 212, 0.06) 0px, transparent 50%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #0b0f19 0%, #111827 100%);
            color: #ffffff; 
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .btn-cyan-glow {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00E5FF, #00f5d4);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.4);
            color: #000000;
            font-weight: 900;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .btn-cyan-glow:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 245, 212, 0.6);
        }
        .btn-cyan-glow:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }

        .cyber-input {
            background: rgba(13, 14, 21, 0.85) !important;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
        }
        .cyber-input:focus {
            border-color: #00E5FF !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.25) !important;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95) !important;
        }

        .diamond-success-toast {
            background-color: #ffffff !important;
            color: #000000 !important;
            border-left: 5px solid #00E5FF;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 10px; }

        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        .spinner { 
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); 
            border-radius: 50%; 
            border-top-color: #00E5FF; 
            width: 44px; 
            height: 44px; 
            animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite; 
        }
        @keyframes pulse-soft {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(0.96); }
        }
        .badge-new { animation: pulse-soft 1.2s infinite; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-3 sm:p-6 flex flex-col justify-start items-center">

    <div id="root" class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto"></div>

    <div id="customAlert" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/85 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-[9999] hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#111827] border-2 border-cyan-500/30 text-white p-6 rounded-2xl max-w-sm w-full text-center space-y-4 shadow-2xl transform scale-100 transition-all">
            <div class="text-4xl">⚠️</div>
            <p id="customAlertText" class="text-sm font-bold leading-relaxed text-gray-200 px-2"></p>
            <button onclick="closeCustomAlert()" class="w-full btn-cyan-glow py-3 rounded-xl text-xs tracking-wider">အိုကေ</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="rulesModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/90 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-[9999] hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#0f1322] border-2 border-red-500/40 text-white p-6 rounded-2xl max-w-md w-full shadow-2xl space-y-4">
            <div class="text-center border-b border-gray-800 pb-3">
                <span class="text-3xl">🚨</span>
                <h3 class="text-red-400 font-black text-base uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">DIAMOND TOP UP MM စည်းကမ်းချက်များ</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-xs leading-relaxed max-h-[50vh] overflow-y-auto pr-1">
                <p class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-yellow-400 block mb-1">၁။ ငွေသွင်းခြင်းအထောက်အထား မှန်ကန်မှုရှိခြင်း</strong> User များအနေဖြင့် Ngwveသွင်းရာတွင် မိမိကိုယ်တိုင် အမှန်တကယ် လွှဲပြောင်းထားသော ပြေစာ (Screenshot) နှင့် မှန်ကန်သော Ngwveသွင်းကုဒ် (Txn Code) နောက်ဆုံး ၆ လုံးကိုသာ တင်ရပါမည်။</p>
                <p class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-red-400 block mb-1">၂။ မမှန်မကန် လုပ်ဆောင်မှုများအပေါ် အရေးယူခြင်း</strong> လိမ်လည်လိုစိတ်ဖြင့် ပြေစာအတုပြုလုပ်ခြင်း၊ သူတစ်ပါး၏ ပြေစာဟောင်းအား ထပ်မံအသုံးပြုခြင်း သို့မဟုတ် ကုဒ်အမှားများကို တမင်သက်သက် ထပ်ခါတလဲလဲ တင်ခြင်းများ ပြုလုပ်ပါက အဆိုပါ User အကောင့်အား မည်သည့်သတိပေးချက်မျှမရှိဘဲ အပြီးပိုင် ပိတ်ပင် (Ban) သွားမည်ဖြစ်သည်။</p>
                <p class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-cyan-400 block mb-1">၃။ အော်ဒါကြာမြင့်ချိန်နှင့် အချိန်သတ်မှတ်ချက်</strong> ပုံမှန်အားဖြင့် အော်ဒါများကို ၁ နာရီအတွင်း အမြန်ဆုံး ဆောင်ရွက်ပေးပါသည်။ သို့သော် ဘဏ်စနစ် (KPay/WavePay) ဒေါင်းနေခြင်း၊ ကွန်ရက်လိုင်းမကောင်းခြင်း သို့မဟုတ် ဂိမ်းဆာဗာပိုင်း ပြဿနာများကြောင့် ကြန့်ကြာမှုရှိနိုင်ပြီး ထိုသို့ဖြစ်ပါက Admin ဘက်မှ အသေးစိတ် စစ်ဆေးပေးမည် ဖြစ်သည်။</p>
                <p class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-emerald-400 block mb-1">၄။ မှာယူမှု ငြင်းပယ်ခံရခြင်း</strong> မိမိဘက်မှ Ngwve မှန်ကန်စွာ လွှဲထားပါလျက် Order ငြင်းပယ်ခံရပါက (သို့မဟုတ်) နားလည်မှုလွဲမှားခြင်းများ ရှိခဲ့ပါက တရားဝင် Telegram Admin ထံသို့ အထောက်အထားအပြည့်အစုံဖြင့် လာရောက်ဖြေရှင်းနိုင်ပါသည်။</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="closeRulesModal()" class="w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-500 text-white text-xs font-black py-3.5 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md">နားလည်ပြီး ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 🔐 CONFIGURATIONS
        const FIREBASE_DB_URL   = 'https://kp-shop-6a917-default-rtdb.asia-southeast1.firebasedatabase.app';
        const TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN = '8719599808:AAHdjf5RoAE0ZfiRDbsr6vrCn7FokQkzxUI'; // Bot Token အသစ်ပြောင်းလဲပြီးပါပြီ
        const TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID   = '8318343193'; 
        const ADMIN_EMAIL        = "188320kopyae@gmail.com";
        const KP_TELEGRAM_LINK   = "https://t.me/kp_gaming_official";

        let dbUsers = {};
        let dbDiamondOrders = {};
        let dbDepositOrders = {};

        let savedActiveUser = localStorage.getItem('kp_active_user_v6') ? JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('kp_active_user_v6')) : null;

        let state = { 
            isLoggedIn: !!savedActiveUser,
            currentUser: savedActiveUser, 
            authMode: 'login', 
            emailInput: '', passwordInput: '', usernameInput: '', 
            gameId: '', zoneId: '', selectedPackage: null, 
            screen: savedActiveUser ? (savedActiveUser.email.toLowerCase() === ADMIN_EMAIL.toLowerCase() ? 'admin_panel' : 'home') : 'auth', 
            screenshotUrl: '', screenshotName: '', isUploadingImage: false, 
            trackingOrder: null, trackingType: 'diamond', selectedDetailOrderId: null, selectedDetailType: 'diamond', selectedPayment: 'kpay', showNoticePopup: true,
            depositAmountInput: '', depositTxCodeInput: '', activeHistoryTab: 'diamond',
            showMlbbCategory: false, 
            adminActiveTab: 'diamond',
            depositStep: 1, 
            depositDisplayPhone: ''
        };

        const packages = [
            { id: 'p1', name: 'Weekly Diamond Pass', price: 7000 },
            { id: 'p2', name: '12 Diamonds', price: 1100 },
            { id: 'p3', name: '21 Diamonds', price: 2000 },
            { id: 'p4', name: '29 Diamonds', price: 2800 },
            { id: 'p5', name: '41 Diamonds', price: 3950 },
            { id: 'p6', name: '202 Diamonds', price: 20000 },
            { id: 'p7', name: '404 Diamonds', price: 35000 },
            { id: 'p8', name: '829 Diamonds', price: 80000 },
            { id: 'p9', name: '2157 Diamonds', price: 210000 },
            { id: 'p10', name: '3489 Diamonds', price: 340000 }
        ];

        window.showAlert = function(message) {
            const alertText = document.getElementById('customAlertText');
            const alertModal = document.getElementById('customAlert');
            if (alertText && alertModal) {
                alertText.innerText = message;
                alertModal.classList.remove('hidden');
            }
        }
        window.closeCustomAlert = function() {
            document.getElementById('customAlert')?.classList.add('hidden');
        }

        window.openRulesModal = function() { document.getElementById('rulesModal')?.classList.remove('hidden'); }
        window.closeRulesModal = function() { document.getElementById('rulesModal')?.classList.add('hidden'); }

        async function fetchAllDataFromFirebase() {
            try {
                const res = await fetch(`${FIREBASE_DB_URL}/.json`);
                const data = await res.json();
                if (data) {
                    dbUsers = data.users || {};
                    dbDiamondOrders = data.diamond_orders || {};
                    dbDepositOrders = data.deposit_orders || {};

                    if (state.isLoggedIn && state.currentUser) {
                        let freshUser = Object.values(dbUsers).find(u => u.id === state.currentUser.id);
                        if (freshUser) {
                            if (freshUser.isBanned) {
                                showAlert("သင့်အကောင့်သည် ပိတ်ပင် (Ban) ခံထားရပါသည်!");
                                handleLogout();
                                return;
                            }
                            state.currentUser = freshUser;
                            localStorage.setItem('kp_active_user_v6', JSON.stringify(freshUser));
                        }
                    }
                }
            } catch (err) {
                console.error("Firebase Sync Error:", err);
            }
        }

        setInterval(() => {
            if (state.screen === 'tracking' && state.trackingOrder) {
                let orderId = state.trackingOrder.orderId;
                let targetNode = state.trackingType === 'diamond' ? dbDiamondOrders[orderId] : dbDepositOrders[orderId];
                if (targetNode && targetNode.status === 'pending') {
                    targetNode.elapsedSeconds = (targetNode.elapsedSeconds || 0) + 1;
                    const timerEl = document.getElementById('liveTimerDisplay');
                    if (timerEl) timerEl.innerText = formatElapsedTime(targetNode.elapsedSeconds);
                }
            }
        }, 1000);

        async function startSyncPulse() {
            await fetchAllDataFromFirebase();
            const activeEl = document.activeElement;
            const isUserTyping = activeEl && (activeEl.tagName === 'INPUT' || activeEl.tagName === 'TEXTAREA');
            if (!isUserTyping) {
                render();
            }
            setTimeout(startSyncPulse, 5000); 
        }

        function formatElapsedTime(seconds) {
            if(!seconds) return "0:00";
            const mins = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
            const secs = seconds % 60;
            return `${mins}:${secs < 10 ? '0' : ''}${secs}`;
        }

        function isIdValid() {
            const cleanGameId = state.gameId.toString().replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');
            const cleanZoneId = state.zoneId.toString().replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');
            return (cleanGameId.length >= 8 && cleanGameId.length <= 11) && (cleanZoneId.length >= 3 && cleanZoneId.length <= 6);
        }

        function hasPendingDiamondOrders() {
            if (!state.currentUser) return false;
            return Object.values(dbDiamondOrders).some(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id && o.status === 'pending');
        }

        function hasPendingDepositOrders() {
            if (!state.currentUser) return false;
            return Object.values(dbDepositOrders).some(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id && o.status === 'pending');
        }

        window.trackInput = function(field, val) {
            state[field] = val;
        }

        window.copyText = function(elementId) {
            let text = document.getElementById(elementId).innerText;
            text = text.replace(" ကျပ်", "");
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
                showAlert("ကူးယူပြီးပါပြီ: " + text);
            });
        }

        window.goToStep2 = function(method) {
            const amount = state.depositAmountInput;
            if (!amount || amount <= 0) {
                showAlert("ကျေးဇူးပြု၍ Ngwveသွင်းပမာဏကို ဖြည့်ပါဗျာ။");
                return;
            }
            state.selectedPayment = method;
            if(method === "kpay") {
                state.depositDisplayPhone = "09671705735"; 
            } else {
                state.depositDisplayPhone = "09668639746"; 
            }
            state.depositStep = 2;
            render();
        }

        window.setAuthMode = function(mode) { state.authMode = mode; render(); }
        window.selectPackage = function(id) { state.selectedPackage = packages.find(p => p.id === id); render(); }
        window.goBack = function() { state.screen = 'home'; render(); }
        window.goToHistoryTab = function(tabType) { state.activeHistoryTab = tabType; state.screen = 'history'; render(); }
        window.switchHistoryTab = function(tab) { state.activeHistoryTab = tab; render(); }
        window.goToProfile = function() { state.screen = 'profile'; render(); }
        window.viewOrderDetails = function(orderId, type) { state.selectedDetailOrderId = orderId; state.selectedDetailType = type; state.screen = 'order_details'; render(); }
        window.backToHomeFromTracking = function() { state.screen = 'home'; render(); }
        window.closeNoticePopup = function() { state.showNoticePopup = false; render(); }
        window.openMlbbCategory = function() { state.showMlbbCategory = true; render(); }
        window.closeMlbbCategory = function() { state.showMlbbCategory = false; render(); }
        window.goToDepositScreen = function() { state.screen = 'deposit_screen'; state.depositStep = 1; render(); }

        window.handleLogout = function() { 
            state.isLoggedIn = false; 
            state.currentUser = null; 
            localStorage.removeItem('kp_active_user_v6'); 
            state.screen = 'auth'; 
            state.authMode = 'login'; 
            render(); 
        }

        window.directGoToCheckout = function() {
            if (!state.selectedPackage) { showAlert("ကျေးဇူးပြု၍ Package တစ်ခုအရင်ရွေးပါဗျာ။"); return; }
            if (!isIdValid()) { showAlert("Game ID (8-11လုံး) နှင့် Zone ID (3-6လုံး) ကိုမှန်အောင်ဖြည့်ပါဗျာ။"); return; }
            state.screen = 'checkout';
            render();
        }

        // 🖼️ IMAGE UPLOAD HANDLE
        window.handleFileUpload = async function(event) {
            const file = event.target.files[0];
            if (!file) return;
            state.isUploadingImage = true;
            render();

            const formData = new FormData();
            formData.append('image', file);

            try {
                // Free Image Hosting API (Imgbb) 
                const res = await fetch('https://api.imgbb.com/1/upload?key=6d207e0211ec7ef30c45f494d16d61af', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    body: formData
                });
                const resData = await res.json();
                if (resData.success) {
                    state.screenshotUrl = resData.data.url;
                    state.screenshotName = file.name;
                } else {
                    showAlert("ပုံတင်ခြင်းမအောင်မြင်ပါ။ ပြန်ကြိုးစားကြည့်ပါ။");
                }
            } catch (err) {
                showAlert("ပုံတင်စဉ် Error တက်သွားပါသည်!");
            } finally {
                state.isUploadingImage = false;
                render();
            }
        }

        // 🔐 AUTH REGISTER & LOGIN SYSTEM
        window.handleAuthSubmit = async function() {
            if(!state.emailInput || !state.passwordInput) { showAlert("အချက်အလက်များကို အကုန်ဖြည့်ပါဗျာ။"); return; }
            if(state.authMode === 'signup' && !state.usernameInput) { showAlert("နာမည်ဖြည့်ပေးပါဗျာ။"); return; }

            await fetchAllDataFromFirebase();
            let allUsers = Object.values(dbUsers);

            if (state.authMode === 'signup') {
                let exist = allUsers.find(u => u.email.toLowerCase() === state.emailInput.toLowerCase());
                if (exist) { showAlert("ဤ Gmail ဖြင့် အကောင့်ဖွင့်ထားပြီးသားဖြစ်နေပါသည်။"); return; }

                let uid = 'USER_' + Math.floor(100000 + Math.random() * 900000);
                let newUser = { id: uid, username: state.usernameInput, email: state.emailInput, password: state.passwordInput, balance: 0, isBanned: false };
                
                await fetch(`${FIREBASE_DB_URL}/users/${uid}.json`, {
                    method: 'PUT',
                    body: JSON.stringify(newUser)
                });
                showAlert("အကောင့်ဖွင့်ခြင်းအောင်မြင်ပါပြီ။");
                state.authMode = 'login';
                render();
            } else {
                let user = allUsers.find(u => u.email.toLowerCase() === state.emailInput.toLowerCase() && u.password === state.passwordInput);
                if (!user) { showAlert("Gmail (သို့) Password မှားယွင်းနေပါသည်!"); return; }
                if (user.isBanned) { showAlert("သင့်အကောင့်မှာ ပိတ်ပင် (Ban) ခံထားရပါသည်!"); return; }

                state.currentUser = user;
                state.isLoggedIn = true;
                localStorage.setItem('kp_active_user_v6', JSON.stringify(user));
                state.screen = 'home';
                render();
            }
        }

        // 💰 (က) CONFIRM DEPOSIT ORDER (ငွေသွင်းမှုပေးပို့ခြင်း)
        window.confirmDepositOrder = async function() {
            if (!state.depositAmountInput || state.depositAmountInput <= 0) { showAlert("ငွေသွင်းပမာဏ မှားယွင်းနေပါသည်။"); return; }
            if (state.depositTxCodeInput.length !== 6) { showAlert("Txn Code နောက်ဆုံး ၆ လုံးကို မှန်ကန်စွာ ဖြည့်ပေးပါဗျာ။"); return; }
            if (!state.screenshotUrl) { showAlert("ကျေးဇူးပြု၍ ငွေလွှဲပြေစာပုံ (Screenshot) တင်ပေးပါဦးဗျာ။"); return; }

            document.getElementById('loadingText')?.classList.remove('hidden');

            let depId = 'DEP_' + Math.floor(100000 + Math.random() * 900000);
            let depositPayload = {
                orderId: depId,
                buyerId: state.currentUser.id,
                buyerName: state.currentUser.username,
                amount: parseFloat(state.depositAmountInput),
                paymentMethod: state.selectedPayment,
                txnCode: state.depositTxCodeInput,
                screenshot: state.screenshotUrl,
                status: 'pending',
                elapsedSeconds: 0,
                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
            };

            try {
                // ၁။ Firebase ထဲ သိမ်းခြင်း
                await fetch(`${FIREBASE_DB_URL}/deposit_orders/${depId}.json`, {
                    method: 'PUT',
                    body: JSON.stringify(depositPayload)
                });

                // ၂။ Telegram Bot ဆီကို Approve/Reject ခလုတ်တွေနှင့်တကွ ပို့ပေးခြင်း
                const inlineKeyboard = {
                    inline_keyboard: [
                        [
                            { text: "✅ Approve (ငွေသွင်းအောင်မြင်)", callback_data: `approve_dep:${depId}:${state.currentUser.id}:${state.depositAmountInput}` },
                            { text: "❌ Reject (ငြင်းပယ်)", callback_data: `reject_dep:${depId}:${state.currentUser.id}` }
                        ]
                    ]
                };

                const textMsg = `🔔 *ငွေသွင်းမှုအသစ် ရောက်ရှိပါသည်။*\n\n👤 User Name: ${state.currentUser.username}\n🆔 User ID: ${state.currentUser.id}\n💰 ပမာဏ: ${state.depositAmountInput} ကျပ်\n🏦 နည်းလမ်း: ${state.selectedPayment.toUpperCase()}\n🔑 Txn Code: ${state.depositTxCodeInput}\n🖼️ ပြေစာပုံ: ${state.screenshotUrl}`;

                await fetch(`https://api.telegram.org/bot${TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}/sendMessage`, {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        chat_id: TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID,
                        text: textMsg,
                        parse_mode: 'Markdown',
                        reply_markup: inlineKeyboard
                    })
                });

                state.trackingOrder = depositPayload;
                state.trackingType = 'deposit';
                state.screen = 'tracking';
                // Reset input inputs
                state.depositAmountInput = ''; state.depositTxCodeInput = ''; state.screenshotUrl = '';
                render();
            } catch (err) {
                showAlert("စနစ်ချို့ယွင်းချက်ဖြစ်သွားပါသည်။ ပြန်ကြိုးစားကြည့်ပါ။");
            }
        }

        // 💎 (ခ) CONFIRM DIAMOND ORDER DIRECT (စိန်ဝယ်ယူမှုပေးပို့ခြင်း)
        window.confirmDiamondOrderDirect = async function() {
            if (!state.selectedPackage) return;
            let price = state.selectedPackage.price;
            if ((state.currentUser.balance || 0) < price) {
                showAlert("သင့် Wallet ထဲတွင် ငွေမလုံလောက်ပါ။ ကျေးဇူးပြု၍ ငွေအရင်သွင်းပါဗျာ။");
                return;
            }

            let ordId = 'DIAMOND_' + Math.floor(100000 + Math.random() * 900000);
            let newBalance = state.currentUser.balance - price;

            // ၁။ ယူဆာပိုက်ဆံ ချက်ချင်းနှုတ်ပြီး Firebase ထဲ သိမ်းခြင်း
            await fetch(`${FIREBASE_DB_URL}/users/${state.currentUser.id}/balance.json`, {
                method: 'PUT',
                body: JSON.stringify(newBalance)
            });
            state.currentUser.balance = newBalance;
            localStorage.setItem('kp_active_user_v6', JSON.stringify(state.currentUser));

            let orderPayload = {
                orderId: ordId,
                buyerId: state.currentUser.id,
                buyerName: state.currentUser.username,
                gameId: state.gameId,
                zoneId: state.zoneId,
                packageName: state.selectedPackage.name,
                price: price,
                status: 'pending',
                elapsedSeconds: 0,
                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
            };

            try {
                await fetch(`${FIREBASE_DB_URL}/diamond_orders/${ordId}.json`, {
                    method: 'PUT',
                    body: JSON.stringify(orderPayload)
                });

                // ၂။ Telegram Bot ဆီကို Approve/Reject ခလုတ်တွေနှင့်တကွ ပို့ပေးခြင်း
                const inlineKeyboard = {
                    inline_keyboard: [
                        [
                            { text: "✅ Diamond ဖြည့်ပြီးပြီ", callback_data: `approve_ord:${ordId}:${state.currentUser.id}` },
                            { text: "❌ Reject (အော်ဒါပယ်/ပြန်အမ်း)", callback_data: `reject_ord:${ordId}:${state.currentUser.id}` }
                        ]
                    ]
                };

                const textMsg = `💎 *စိန်ဝယ်ယူမှုအသစ် ရောက်ရှိပါသည်။*\n\n🛒 Item: ${state.selectedPackage.name}\n🆔 Game ID: ${state.gameId} (${state.zoneId})\n💰 နှုတ်ယူသည့်ငွေ: ${price} ကျပ်\n👤 ဝယ်သူ Name: ${state.currentUser.username}\n👤 User UID: ${state.currentUser.id}`;

                await fetch(`https://api.telegram.org/bot${TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}/sendMessage`, {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        chat_id: TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID,
                        text: textMsg,
                        parse_mode: 'Markdown',
                        reply_markup: inlineKeyboard
                    })
                });

                state.trackingOrder = orderPayload;
                state.trackingType = 'diamond';
                state.screen = 'tracking';
                render();
            } catch (err) {
                showAlert("အော်ဒါတင်စဉ် အမှားအယွင်းတစ်ခုရှိခဲ့ပါသည်။");
            }
        }

        // 📋 RENDER APP SCREENS & HISTORIES
        function render() {
            // (အပေါ်က Render ပုံစံအတိုင်း စနစ်တကျ ပြန်လည်အလုပ်လုပ်ပေးမည့် အပိုင်း)
            // [မှတ်ချက် - ကုဒ်ရှုပ်ထွေးမှုမရှိစေရန် render logic မူရင်းအတိုင်း တိကျစွာ ဆက်လက်ထိန်းသိမ်းထားသည်]
            const root = document.getElementById('root');
            if (!root) return;
            
            if (!state.isLoggedIn) {
                // ပြသပေးမည့် Auth Form (Login/Signup)
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="glass-panel p-6 mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/20">
                        <h2 class="text-[#00E5FF] text-3xl font-black text-center mb-1 tracking-wider uppercase drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,229,255,0.4)]">KP DIAMOND</h2>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center mb-6">စနစ်ကိုအသုံးပြုရန် အကောင့်ဝင်ပေးပါဗျာ</p>
                        <div class="flex bg-black/40 p-1.5 rounded-xl mb-6 border border-white/5">
                            <button onclick="setAuthMode('login')" class="w-full py-2.5 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg transition-all ${state.authMode === 'login' ? 'bg-[#00E5FF]/10 text-[#00E5FF] border border-[#00E5FF]/20' : 'text-gray-400'}">လော့ဂ်အင်ဝင်ရန်</button>
                            <button onclick="setAuthMode('signup')" class="w-full py-2.5 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg transition-all ${state.authMode === 'signup' ? 'bg-[#00E5FF]/10 text-[#00E5FF] border border-[#00E5FF]/20' : 'text-gray-400'}">အကောင့်သစ်ဖွင့်ရန်</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                            ${state.authMode === 'signup' ? `
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5 pl-1">နာမည် (Username)</label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="ဥပမာ - U Kyaw Ko" value="${state.usernameInput}" oninput="trackInput('usernameInput', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none">
                            </div>` : ''}
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5 pl-1">Gmail လိပ်စာ</label>
                                <input type="email" placeholder="example@gmail.com" value="${state.emailInput}" oninput="trackInput('emailInput', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1.5 pl-1">လျှို့ဝှက်နံပါတ် (Password)</label>
                                <input type="password" placeholder="••••••••" value="${state.passwordInput}" oninput="trackInput('passwordInput', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="handleAuthSubmit()" class="w-full btn-cyan-glow py-4 rounded-xl text-sm tracking-wide">
                            ${state.authMode === 'login' ? 'ENTER APP (ဝင်မည်)' : 'CREATE ACCOUNT (အကောင့်ဖွင့်မည်)'}
                        </button>
                    </div>`;
                return;
            }

            let showDiamondNew = hasPendingDiamondOrders();
            let showDepositNew = hasPendingDepositOrders();
            let headerBlock = `
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 glass-panel p-4 rounded-2xl mb-4 border border-cyan-500/10 shadow-xl">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <div onclick="goToProfile()" class="text-xs cursor-pointer hover:opacity-80 flex items-center gap-2.5">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00E5FF] to-[#00f5d4] flex items-center justify-center text-black font-black text-lg shadow-lg">
                                ${state.currentUser.username ? state.currentUser.username.charAt(0).toUpperCase() : 'U'}
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-gray-100 font-black text-sm">👤 ${state.currentUser.username}</p>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-mono font-bold mt-0.5">${state.currentUser.id}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                            <button onclick="goToHistoryTab('diamond')" class="relative text-[10px] bg-black/40 hover:bg-black/60 border border-cyan-500/20 px-2.5 py-2 rounded-xl text-cyan-400 font-bold transition-all flex items-center gap-1">
                                <span>စိန်မှတ်တမ်း</span>
                                ${showDiamondNew ? `<span class="badge-new bg-red-500 text-white text-[9px] px-1 rounded-sm scale-90 font-mono">New</span>` : ''}
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="goToHistoryTab('deposit')" class="relative text-[10px] bg-black/40 hover:bg-black/60 border border-emerald-500/20 px-2.5 py-2 rounded-xl text-emerald-400 font-bold transition-all flex items-center gap-1">
                                <span>ငွေသွင်းမှတ်တမ်း</span>
                                ${showDepositNew ? `<span class="badge-new bg-red-500 text-white text-[9px] px-1 rounded-sm scale-90 font-mono">New</span>` : ''}
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button onclick="openRulesModal()" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-red-950/60 to-red-900/60 border border-red-500/30 text-red-200 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-black tracking-wide shadow flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-95 transition-all">
                        <span>🚨</span> စည်းကမ်းချက်များ ဖတ်ရှုရန် <span>🚨</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0d1624] to-[#090f1a] border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-xl p-3.5 flex justify-between items-center mt-1">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Wallet Balance</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-black text-emerald-400 font-mono mt-0.5">${(state.currentUser.balance || 0)} Ks</p>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="goToDepositScreen()" class="text-xs bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 border border-emerald-600 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-black font-black transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                            💰 ငွေသွင်းမည်
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>`;

            if (state.screen === 'home') {
                if (!state.showMlbbCategory) {
                    root.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="relative w-full">
                            ${state.showNoticePopup ? `
                            <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/85 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
                                <div class="bg-[#111827] border border-cyan-500/20 text-white p-6 rounded-2xl max-w-sm w-full text-center space-y-4 shadow-2xl">
                                    <div class="text-3xl">📢</div>
                                    <h3 class="font-black text-base tracking-wide text-[#00E5FF] border-b border-white/5 pb-2">အရေးကြီးသတိပေးချက်</h3>
                                    <p class="text-xs font-bold leading-relaxed text-gray-300 text-left">မနက် 8 နာရီမှ ည 10 နာရီ အတွင်း Order တင်ပါက အချိန်တိုအတွင်း လျင်မြန်စွာ ရောက်ရှိနိုင်ပါတယ်ဗျာ။ အကယ်၍ အခက်အခဲများ ကြုံတွေ့ရပါက Kp First နဲ့ တိုက်ရိုက် ဆက်သွယ်ပေးပါဗျာ။</p>
                                    <div class="space-y-2 pt-2">
                                        <a href="${KP_TELEGRAM_LINK}" target="_blank" class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-bold py-3 rounded-xl block text-center transition-all">💬 Kp First နှင့် တိုက်ရိုက်ပြောမည်</a>
                                        <button onclick="closeNoticePopup()" class="w-full bg-white text-black text-xs font-black py-2.5 rounded-xl">နားလည်ပါပြီ ဆက်သွားရန်</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>` : ''}
                            ${headerBlock}
                            <div class="mt-6">
                                <button onclick="openMlbbCategory()" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#111827] to-[#1f2937] hover:from-[#1f2937] hover:to-[#374151] border-2 border-[#00E5FF] text-[#00E5FF] font-black py-10 rounded-2xl text-base tracking-wide shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-all active:scale-95 duration-200">
                                    <span class="text-4xl filter drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,229,255,0.5)]">💎🎮💎</span>
                                    <span class="font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00E5FF] to-[#00f5d4]">Mobile Legends Diamonds</span>
                                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-normal">စိန်ဝယ်ယူရန် ဤနေရာကိုနှိပ်ပါ</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>`;
                } else {
                    let packageCards = packages.map(pkg => {
                        const isSelected = state.selectedPackage?.id === pkg.id;
                        return `
                            <div onclick="selectPackage('${pkg.id}')" class="p-4 rounded-xl text-center cursor-pointer border-2 transition-all ${isSelected ? 'border-[#00E5FF] bg-[#00E5FF]/5 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,229,255,0.1)]' : 'border-transparent bg-black/30'}">
                                <div class="font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-200">${pkg.name}</div>
                                <div class="text-[#00E5FF] mt-1.5 text-xs font-black font-mono">${pkg.price} Ks</div>
                            </div>`;
                    }).join('');

                    root.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="pb-36 relative w-full">
                            ${headerBlock}
                            <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between bg-black/40 border border-[#00E5FF]/20 p-3 rounded-xl">
                                <span class="text-[#00E5FF] text-xs font-black tracking-wider">🎮 MOBILE LEGENDS SHOP</span>
                                <button onclick="closeMlbbCategory()" class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 font-bold underline hover:text-white">← ဆိုင်ပိတ်မည်</button>
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 text-gray-400 pl-1">၁။ PACKAGE (စိန်) အရင်ရွေးချယ်ပါ</h4>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2.5 mb-5">${packageCards}</div>
                            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl mb-6 shadow-lg border border-white/5">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 text-gray-400 pl-1">၂။ GAME ID ဖြည့်ပါ</h4>
                                <div class="flex gap-2">
                                    <input type="number" pattern="[0-9]*" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="User ID (8-11 လုံး)" value="${state.gameId}" oninput="trackInput('gameId', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none">
                                    <input type="number" pattern="[0-9]*" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="Zone ID" value="${state.zoneId}" oninput="trackInput('zoneId', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="fixed bottom-4 left-2 right-2 glass-panel border border-[#00E5FF]/20 p-4 max-w-md mx-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl z-40">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">စုစုပေါင်းကျသင့်ငွေ</div>
                                        <div class="text-xl font-black text-[#00E5FF] font-mono">${state.selectedPackage ? state.selectedPackage.price : 0} Ks</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <button onclick="directGoToCheckout()" class="btn-cyan-glow text-black font-black px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">ဝယ်ယူရန်</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>`;
                }
            } 
            else if (state.screen === 'deposit_screen') {
                let paymentName = state.selectedPayment === 'kpay' ? 'U Kyaw Ko (KPay)' : 'U Kyaw Ko (Wave Pay)';
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="pb-12 w-full">
                        <h3 class="text-emerald-400 text-lg font-black mb-4 text-center tracking-wider">WALLET အတွင်းသို့ ငွေသွင်းမည်</h3>
                        <div id="step1" class="${state.depositStep === 1 ? '' : 'hidden'} space-y-4">
                            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/5">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">၁။ ငွေသွင်းမည့် ပမာဏကို ရိုက်ထည့်ပါ</h4>
                                <input type="number" id="amountInput" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="ဥပမာ - ၁၀၀၀၀" value="${state.depositAmountInput}" oninput="trackInput('depositAmountInput', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-400">
                            </div>
                            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/5">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">၂။ ငွေသွင်းမည့် နည်းလမ်းကို ရွေးချယ်ပါ</h4>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                    <button onclick="goToStep2('kpay')" class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/10 hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-all font-black text-white text-xs tracking-wide">KBZ Pay ဖြင့် ဆက်သွားရန်</button>
                                    <button onclick="goToStep2('wave')" class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-500/10 hover:bg-amber-500/20 transition-all font-black text-white text-xs tracking-wide">Wave Pay ဖြင့် ဆက်သွားရန်</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="step2" class="${state.depositStep === 2 ? '' : 'hidden'} space-y-4">
                            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/5 space-y-3.5">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">ငွေလွှဲရန် အသေးစိတ်အချက်အလက်များ</h4>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-black/40 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase">လွှဲရမည့် ပမာဏ</p>
                                        <p id="displayAmount" class="text-base text-emerald-400 font-black font-mono">${state.depositAmountInput} ကျပ်</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <button onclick="copyText('displayAmount')" class="bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded font-black">Copy</button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-black/40 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase">လွှဲရမည့် ဖုန်းနံပါတ် (<span id="methodName" class="uppercase">${state.selectedPayment}</span>)</p>
                                        <p id="displayPhone" class="text-base text-cyan-400 font-mono font-black tracking-wider">${state.depositDisplayPhone}</p>
                                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-0.5">အမည် - ${paymentName}</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <button onclick="copyText('displayPhone')" class="bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-400 text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded font-black">Copy</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/5 space-y-4">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">ငွေသွင်းအထောက်အထား ဖြည့်သွင်းပါ</h4>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-[11px] text-gray-400 mb-1.5 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">လုပ်ငန်းစဉ်ကုဒ် နောက်ဆုံး ၆ လုံး (Txn Code)</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="codeInput" maxlength="6" placeholder="ဥပမာ - ၁၂၃၄၅၆" value="${state.depositTxCodeInput}" oninput="trackInput('depositTxCodeInput', this.value)" class="w-full p-3.5 rounded-xl cyber-input text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-400">
                                </div>
                                <div class="relative w-full bg-black/40 border border-dashed border-emerald-500/30 rounded-xl py-5 px-4 text-center cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-black/60 transition-all">
                                    <input type="file" id="imageInput" accept="image/*" onchange="handleFileUpload(event)" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-0 cursor-pointer">
                                    <span id="imageUploadLabel" class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-black tracking-wide">
                                        ${state.isUploadingImage ? '⏳ ပုံတင်နေပါသည်...' : (state.screenshotUrl ? `✓ ပုံတင်ခြင်းအောင်မြင်ပါပြီ` : '📸 ငွေသွင်း ပြေစာပုံတင်ရန် (Upload Screenshot)')}
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <button id="submitBtn" onclick="confirmDepositOrder()" class="w-full bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-black font-black py-4 rounded-xl text-sm tracking-wide shadow-xl transition-all">အော်ဒါ အတည်ပြုရန်</button>
                            <button onclick="state.depositStep = 1; render();" class="w-full bg-transparent text-gray-400 font-bold py-1 text-xs hover:text-white underline">← အဆင့် ၁ သို့ ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="goBack()" class="w-full bg-transparent text-gray-500 font-bold py-2 mt-4 text-xs hover:text-white">ပင်မစာမျက်နှာသို့ ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
                    </div>`;
            }
            else if (state.screen === 'checkout') {
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="pb-12 w-full">
                        <h3 class="text-[#00E5FF] text-lg font-black mb-4 text-center tracking-wider">ဝယ်ယူမှု အတည်ပြုခြင်း</h3>
                        <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-4 border border-white/5 space-y-2.5">
                            <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-[#00E5FF] mb-3 border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5 uppercase tracking-wider">မှာယူမှု အသေးစိတ်</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">ဝယ်ယူသူ - <span class="text-white font-black">${state.currentUser.username}</span></p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Game ID: <span class="text-white font-mono font-bold bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-white/5">${state.gameId} (${state.zoneId})</span></p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Package: <span class="text-white font-black text-yellow-400">${state.selectedPackage?.name}</span></p>
                            <p class="text-base text-[#00E5FF] font-black pt-1">ကျသင့်ငွေ: ${state.selectedPackage?.price} Ks</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6 text-center space-y-2 border border-white/5">
                            <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-400 font-medium">သင့်အကောင့်လက်ကျန်ငွေမှ တိုက်ရိုက်နှုတ်ယူသွားမည်ဖြစ်ပြီး စခရင်ရှော့ပုံ တင်ရန်မလိုပါဗျာ။</p>
                            <div class="text-sm font-black text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/5 py-2 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/10">လက်ရှိအကောင့်လက်ကျန်: ${(state.currentUser.balance || 0)} Ks</div>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="confirmDiamondOrderDirect()" class="w-full btn-cyan-glow py-4 rounded-xl text-sm tracking-wide">မှာယူမှုကို အတည်ပြုပါ</button>
                        <button onclick="goBack()" class="w-full bg-transparent text-gray-500 font-bold py-2 mt-2 text-xs hover:text-white">နောက်သို့ ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
                    </div>`;
            }
            else if (state.screen === 'tracking') {
                let orderId = state.trackingOrder?.orderId;
                let currentOrder = state.trackingType === 'diamond' ? dbDiamondOrders[orderId] : dbDepositOrders[orderId];
                if (!currentOrder) currentOrder = { status: 'pending', elapsedSeconds: 0 };
                
                let statusText = "စောင့်ဆိုင်းနေဆဲ (PENDING)";
                let statusBadgeColor = "text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20";
                let customOutputHTML = "";

                if (currentOrder.status === 'completed' || currentOrder.status === 'success') {
                    statusText = "SUCCESS";
                    statusBadgeColor = "text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl font-black text-base";
                    if (state.trackingType === 'deposit') {
                        customOutputHTML = `<div class="p-4 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-emerald-400 leading-relaxed text-left">အောင်မြင်ပါသည်။ သင်သည်အချက်အလက်များမှန်ကန်စွာဖြည့်ခဲ့သဖြင့် အောင်မြင်ပါသည်။ နောက်ထပ်လည်း မျှော်လင့်ပါသည်။</div>`;
                    } else {
                        customOutputHTML = `<div class="p-5 diamond-success-toast rounded-xl text-sm font-black leading-relaxed text-left shadow-lg">သင့်အကောင့်အား diamond (${currentOrder.packageName ? currentOrder.packageName.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '') : 'Pass'}) ထည့်သွင်းထားပါသည်။ သွားရောက်စစ်ဆေးကြည့်ပေးပါအုန်းဗျာ။</div>`;
                    }
                }
                if (currentOrder.status === 'rejected') {
                    statusText = "❌ REJECTED";
                    statusBadgeColor = "text-red-400 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl font-black text-base";
                    if (state.trackingType === 'deposit') {
                        customOutputHTML = `<div class="p-4 bg-red-950/40 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-red-400 leading-relaxed text-left">ငွေလွှဲကုဒ် သို့မဟုတ် ပြေစာအချက်အလက် မှားယွင်းနေပါသည်။ ကျေးပြု၍ ပြန်လည်စစ်ဆေးပေးပါဗျာ။</div>`;
                    } else {
                        customOutputHTML = `<div class="p-4 bg-red-950/40 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-red-400 leading-relaxed space-y-3"><p>တစ်ခုခုလွဲလျော်သွားခြင်း (သို့) admin ဘက်မှ မှားယွင်းဖယ်ချခြင်းများလုပ်မိသွားပါသည်။ admin သို့ချက်ချင်း အကြောင်းကြားရန်</p><a href="${KP_TELEGRAM_LINK}" target="_blank" class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-center font-black py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-all">💬 Contact Admin Telegram</a></div>`;
                    }
                }

                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="text-center mt-6 w-full space-y-4">
                        <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl space-y-6 border border-white/5">
                            ${(currentOrder.status === 'pending') ? `<div class="flex justify-center my-4"><div class="spinner"></div></div>` : ''}
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold">Order ID: <span class="font-mono text-white font-black bg-black/40 px-2 py-1 rounded">${orderId}</span></div>
                            <div class="text-sm font-black tracking-wider py-1.5 px-3 rounded-lg inline-block ${statusBadgeColor}">${statusText}</div>
                            
                            ${currentOrder.status === 'pending' ? `
                            <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl">
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">အော်ဒါစစ်ဆေးနေသည့် ကြာမြင့်ချိန်</p>
                                <p id="liveTimerDisplay" class="text-3xl font-black text-cyan-400 font-mono mt-1">${formatElapsedTime(currentOrder.elapsedSeconds)}</p>
                            </div>` : ''}

                            ${customOutputHTML}
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="backToHomeFromTracking()" class="w-full bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white font-black py-3.5 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wide transition-all shadow-md">← ပင်မစာမျက်နှာသို့ ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
                    </div>`;
            }
            else if (state.screen === 'history') {
                // (မှတ်တမ်းများပြသပေးမည့် မျက်နှာပြင်)
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="w-full pb-12">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                            <button onclick="goBack()" class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-gray-300">← ပြန်ထွက်</button>
                            <h3 class="text-md font-black">📜 မှာယူမှုမှတ်တမ်းများ</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex bg-black/40 p-1 rounded-xl mb-4 border border-white/5">
                            <button onclick="switchHistoryTab('diamond')" class="w-full py-2 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg ${state.activeHistoryTab === 'diamond' ? 'bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 border border-cyan-500/20' : 'text-gray-400'}">စိန်မှတ်တမ်း</button>
                            <button onclick="switchHistoryTab('deposit')" class="w-full py-2 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg ${state.activeHistoryTab === 'deposit' ? 'bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/20' : 'text-gray-400'}">ငွေသွင်းမှတ်တမ်း</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2.5">
                            ${state.activeHistoryTab === 'diamond' ? 
                                (Object.values(dbDiamondOrders).filter(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id).length === 0 ? `<p class="text-xs text-center text-gray-500 py-6">စိန်ဝယ်ယူထားခြင်း မရှိသေးပါဗျာ။</p>` : 
                                Object.values(dbDiamondOrders).filter(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id).reverse().map(o => `
                                    <div onclick="viewOrderDetails('${o.orderId}', 'diamond')" class="p-3.5 rounded-xl glass-panel flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer border border-white/5 hover:border-cyan-500/30">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-200">${o.packageName}</p>
                                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-mono mt-0.5">${o.orderId}</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase ${o.status==='pending'?'text-amber-400':(o.status==='rejected'?'text-red-400':'text-green-400')}">${o.status}</span>
                                    </div>`).join(''))
                                :
                                (Object.values(dbDepositOrders).filter(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id).length === 0 ? `<p class="text-xs text-center text-gray-500 py-6">ငွေသွင်းထားခြင်း မရှိသေးပါဗျာ။</p>` : 
                                Object.values(dbDepositOrders).filter(o => o.buyerId === state.currentUser.id).reverse().map(o => `
                                    <div onclick="viewOrderDetails('${o.orderId}', 'deposit')" class="p-3.5 rounded-xl glass-panel flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer border border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="text-xs font-black text-emerald-400">+${o.amount} Ks</p>
                                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-mono mt-0.5">${o.orderId}</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase ${o.status==='pending'?'text-amber-400':(o.status==='rejected'?'text-red-400':'text-green-400')}">${o.status}</span>
                                    </div>`).join(''))
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>`;
            }
            else if (state.screen === 'order_details') {
                let targetOrd = state.selectedDetailType === 'diamond' ? dbDiamondOrders[state.selectedDetailOrderId] : dbDepositOrders[state.selectedDetailOrderId];
                if (!targetOrd) { root.innerHTML=`<p class="text-xs text-center text-red-400 py-8">Order Data Not Found.</p>`; return; }
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="glass-panel p-5 rounded-2xl w-full space-y-4">
                        <div class="border-b border-white/5 pb-2.5 flex justify-between items-center">
                            <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#00E5FF]">📋 ORDER DETAILS</h3>
                            <button onclick="state.screen='history'; render();" class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-white">← ပြန်သွားရန်</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2 text-xs text-gray-300">
                            <p>Order ID: <span class="font-mono text-white font-bold">${targetOrd.orderId}</span></p>
                            <p>အမျိုးအစား: <span class="text-white font-bold uppercase">${state.selectedDetailType}</span></p>
                            <p>လက်ရှိအခြေအနေ: <span class="font-black uppercase text-yellow-400">${targetOrd.status}</span></p>
                            ${state.selectedDetailType === 'diamond' ? `
                                <p>ဂိမ်း ID: <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono font-bold">${targetOrd.gameId} (${targetOrd.zoneId})</span></p>
                                <p>အစီအစဉ်: <span class="text-white font-bold">${targetOrd.packageName}</span></p>
                                <p>ကျသင့်ငွေ: <span class="text-white font-bold">${targetOrd.price} Ks</span></p>
                            ` : `
                                <p>ပမာဏ: <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">${targetOrd.amount} Ks</span></p>
                                <p>ငွေလွှဲကုဒ်: <span class="text-white font-mono font-bold">${targetOrd.txnCode}</span></p>
                                <p>ဘဏ်စနစ်: <span class="text-white uppercase font-bold">${targetOrd.paymentMethod}</span></p>
                            `}
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 pt-2 font-mono">အချိန်: ${new Date(targetOrd.timestamp).toLocaleString()}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>`;
            }
            else if (state.screen === 'profile') {
                root.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-2xl w-full text-center space-y-4">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-cyan-400 to-emerald-400 flex items-center justify-center text-black font-black text-2xl shadow-xl">
                            ${state.currentUser.username ? state.currentUser.username.charAt(0).toUpperCase() : 'U'}
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-black text-base text-white">👤 ${state.currentUser.username}</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono font-bold mt-0.5">${state.currentUser.email}</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-black/30 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 text-left text-xs space-y-1.5">
                            <p class="text-gray-400">User ID: <span class="font-mono font-bold text-white">${state.currentUser.id}</span></p>
                            <p class="text-gray-400">Wallet Balance: <span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">${state.currentUser.balance || 0} Ks</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-2 space-y-2">
                            <button onclick="goBack()" class="w-full bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold transition-all">← ပင်မစာမျက်နှာသို့</button>
                            <button onclick="handleLogout()" class="w-full bg-red-600/20 hover:bg-red-600 text-red-400 hover:text-white border border-red-500/20 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold transition-all">🚪 အကောင့်ထဲမှ ထွက်မည်</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>`;
            }
        }

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            startSyncPulse();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
